5
00:00:07,224 --> 00:00:09,976
<i>Kakekku bukan seorang penjaga.
Dia adalah narapidana.</i>

6
00:00:11,095 --> 00:00:12,629
<i>Itu dia.</i>

7
00:00:12,696 --> 00:00:13,813
