00:00:18,519 --> 00:00:20,186
<i>Kita harus menemukan siapa yang membawa mereka.</i>

12
00:00:20,271 --> 00:00:21,804
<i>Jack, turunkan pistolmu!
/Lakukan!</i>

13
00:00:21,856 --> 00:00:24,274
<i>Berlutut!
