36
00:01:36,080 --> 00:01:39,882
Petualangan.
Ini cerita klasik modern.

37
00:01:39,934 --> 00:01:43,019
Salah satu kesukaan Dr. Sangupta,

38
00:01:43,070 --> 00:01:44,720
