70
00:04:04,745 --> 00:04:06,212
Aku butuh bantuan.

71
00:04:06,296 --> 00:04:09,932
Bunuhlah tupai besar yang pandai
melompat di sana.

72
00:04:13,837 --> 00:04:16,706
Grindle si pustakawan?

73
