dia meracuni orang.

148
00:08:02,979 --> 00:08:04,329
Dia sering menggunakan Sianida.

149
00:08:04,380 --> 00:08:06,464
Awalnya sedikit lalu bertambah banyak,

150
00:08:06,515 --> 00:08:08,683
